cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.SD, cs.SY, cs.LG

Reasoning: 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is the most likely category as the paper discusses the creation of a real-time recommendation system using data collected from Last.fm. 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is also likely as the paper characterizes users' profiles, including their friends and country. 
- cs.SD (Software Engineering) is a possibility as the paper discusses the evaluation of the co-occurrence of songs in users' histories, which can be used to compute similarity between songs. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possibility as the paper discusses the creation of a real-time recommendation system. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possibility as the paper discusses the computation of similarity between songs, which could involve machine learning techniques.
